tourguide.service

Interface ServiceLocationFeignClient


  • @FeignClient(name="tourguide-service-location",
             url="localhost:8081")
public interface ServiceLocationFeignClient
    ServiceLocationFeignClient is used by Feign to build http request.
    The target of the request is the Service-Location service.
    For more details concerning the request, see TourGuideController.
